[
    {
        "content": "<p>Rebasing to v6.11-rc1 I found <a href=\"https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux.git/commit/include/linux/platform_device.h?id=0edb555a65d1ef047a9805051c36922b52a38a9d\">this mainline change</a></p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"n\">int</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">remove</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">platform_device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"n\">void</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">remove_new</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">platform_device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"k\">union</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">       </span><span class=\"n\">void</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">remove</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">platform_device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">       </span><span class=\"n\">void</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">remove_new</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">platform_device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>to confuse bindgen: The resulting  <code>rust/bindings/bindings_generated.rs</code> doesn't contain <code>remove()</code> any more but just <code>pub __bindgen_anon_1: platform_driver__bindgen_ty_1,</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[repr(C)]</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#[derive(Copy, Clone)]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">platform_driver</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">probe</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">option</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nb\">Option</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">extern</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"C\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">arg1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">platform_device</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ffi</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">c_int</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__bindgen_anon_1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">platform_driver__bindgen_ty_1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">shutdown</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">option</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nb\">Option</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">extern</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"C\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">arg1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">platform_device</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">pub</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">suspend</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">option</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nb\">Option</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">unsafe</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">extern</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"C\"</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">arg1</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"k\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">platform_device</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">state</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">pm_message_t</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">core</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ffi</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">c_int</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Anything more clever what could be done to fix that? Besides reverting the mainline commit?</p>",
        "id": 457038030,
        "sender_full_name": "Dirk Behme",
        "timestamp": 1723016856
